<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Snowball_Earth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=31" title="Edit section: Notes and references">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Notes and references</span></h2>
<div class="references-small references-column-count references-column-count-2" style="-moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;">
<ol class="references">
