<li id="cite_note-Williams-67"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Williams_67-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFWilliams_G.E..3B_Schmidt_P.W.1997">Williams G.E.; Schmidt P.W. (1997). "<a href="http://www.cosis.net/abstracts/EAE03/08262/EAE03-J-08262.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.cosis.net/abstracts/EAE03/08262/EAE03-J-08262.pdf" rel="nofollow">Paleomagnetism of the Paleoproterozoic Gowganda and Lorrain formations, Ontario: low palaeolatitude for Huronian glaciation</a>" (PDF). <i>EPSL</i> <b>153</b> (3): 157–169. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1016%2FS0012-821X%2897%2900181-7" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1016%2FS0012-821X%2897%2900181-7" rel="nofollow">10.1016/S0012-821X(97)00181-7</a></span><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.cosis.net/abstracts/EAE03/08262/EAE03-J-08262.pdf" class="external free" title="http://www.cosis.net/abstracts/EAE03/08262/EAE03-J-08262.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www.cosis.net/abstracts/EAE03/08262/EAE03-J-08262.pdf</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Paleomagnetism+of+the+Paleoproterozoic+Gowganda+and+Lorrain+formations%2C+Ontario%3A+low+palaeolatitude+for+Huronian+glaciation&amp;rft.jtitle=EPSL&amp;rft.aulast=Williams+G.E.%3B+Schmidt+P.W.&amp;rft.au=Williams+G.E.%3B+Schmidt+P.W.&amp;rft.date=1997&amp;rft.volume=153&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=157%E2%80%93169&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1016%2FS0012-821X%2897%2900181-7&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosis.net%2Fabstracts%2FEAE03%2F08262%2FEAE03-J-08262.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Snowball_Earth"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
